response.overview: Go on the journey of E'Lease finding herself in choosing her career or staying where she is underappreciated. Through some self-reflection and suggestion from her family and friend... E'Lease purchases the Ease Your Mind Journal Series Everyday Life Struggles The Basics to find her way.
